# elementType

**Instance Property**

The type of each element in the data.

## Declaration

```swift
var elementType: VNElementType { get }
```

## Determining Types of Feature Prints

- **VNElementType**: An enumeration of the type of element in feature print data.
- **VNElementTypeSize(_:)**: Returns the size of a feature print element.
